Rating: 0
Both the recipe AND the picture show the crabmeat folded into the creme fraiche mixture. If a reviewer (ex: "A Cook from Carbondale") gives a recipe a low rating, when they haven't followed the recipe as written, then the review is misleading. Changing the amount of salt can be a matter of taste preference, whereas changing the technique and then writing a negative review is an entirely different matter -- just my opinion of course.

